8. Identify misplaced items on the dining table.

10. Put the box of crackers in the cabinet.
11. Put the mug in the cabinet.
12. Put the glass in the cabinet.
13. Put the knife in the designated knife storage.
14. Put the lemons in the designated fruit storage or a bowl if available.
15. Inspect the sink area to ensure it's clear of clutter.
16. Verify all items are in their correct storage locations.
17. Confirm the kitchen is organized.
